	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=92560><span id=Scholar>agonizer</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>223 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [2.72]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Besides being Ultra rare as everyone is saying isnt the focus a bit retarded except for being a twink item?<br>Per Allahkazam the Improved Damage I Description: <br>1: Increases spell effectiveness up to 20%<br>2: Restriction: Spells level 20 and lower<br>3: Restriction: Only applies to 'Hit Points (HP)' spells<br>4: Restriction: Affects 'Instant' spells only<br>5: Restriction: 'Detrimental' spells only<br>6: Restriction: 'Location Based AoE' spells excluded<br>7: Restriction: 'Point Blank AoE' spells excluded<br>8: Restriction: 'Target Based AoE' spells excluded<br>9: Restriction: 'Giants' spells excluded<br>10: Restriction: 'Dragons' spells excluded<br><br>From what I understand the focus only affects spells that are under level 20, yet this drops off a level 30 mob and would be useless for non-spell casting classes such as Warriors.<br><br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Oct&nbsp;&nbsp;8 00:44:46 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br><span style='color: Maroon;'><a href=HTTP://www.angelfire.com/cantina/zraptor/ target=akztarg>Zraptors Helping Hand</a> is my attempt to help others (like my posts here) in a more personal way. Feel free to browse my website, post in my forum or email me for help. Good luck.</td></td></tr>
